    <h1 class="cs-h2" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px); max-width: 900px;">Reducing Operational Friction to Unlock Marketplace Supply</h1>
    <p class="cs-hero-sub">Replaced a multi-step inventory hierarchy with a persistent filter workspace, bringing listed and unlisted gear into one continuous management flow.</p>

    <div class="cs-divider-grid cs-divider-grid--hero">
      <div>
        <div class="cs-label">COMPARATIVE WORKFLOW TESTING</div>
        <div class="cs-stat-value--sm">~3<span class="accent">&times;</span> <span style="font: 400 italic clamp(18px, 2vw, 24px) var(--serif); color: var(--text-faint)">faster</span></div>
